rComments: I loved Najat! She is very caring and wants her students to succeed. The class is very well organized and the grading criteria are clear. She is open to her students' suggestions. The only downside is that her lectures were not recorded so if you missed a class, you needed to borrow notes from another student.
She is awesome, very caring about the student, really easy to understand she takes her time and made everything clear. She is a future incredible professor.
